### Subscriptions API Tests
### Base URL
@baseUrl = http://localhost:4080/api/v1

### Login to get token
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@cody.inc",
  "password": "password"
}

### Set token from login response
@token = {{login.response.body.token}}

### ==================================================
### SUBSCRIPTIONS ENDPOINTS
### ==================================================

### Subscribe to a Plan
# @name subscribe
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/subscribe
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "plan_id": 1,
  "auto_renew": true
}

### Get All Subscriptions (Admin)
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Current Active Subscription
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/my-subscription
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get My Subscription History
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/my-history
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Subscription by ID
@subscriptionId = {{subscribe.response.body.id}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update Subscription
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "auto_renew": false
}

### Activate Subscription (after payment)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/activate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Suspend Subscription (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/suspend
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Renew Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/renew
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Cancel Subscription
POST {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}/cancel
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "cancellation_reason": "No longer need the service"
}

### Delete Subscription
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/{{subscriptionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ==================================================
### USAGE ENDPOINTS (TRV-032)
### ==================================================

### Get Subscription Usage Stats
# @name getUsage
# Returns current usage vs plan limits
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions/usage
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
